data.description: Nestled in a well-established neighborhood, this property exudes potential and exceptional value. This duplex does require some finishing touches its solid bones and prime location make it a standout investment. Each unit boasts spacious living areas and ample natural light.  The duplex presents a unique opportunity for a first time Buyer looking for an income producing property with long term Tenants. Motivated Seller. AS IS.   First Floor Unit is 2 Bedroom , 1 Bath and will be delivered empty  Second Floor Unit is 3 Bedroom , 2 Bath and Tenant occupied until August 2024
